node.text:
Our team set off to be part of the world’s largest trail clean up, Oregon’s Gambler 500. With a team of engineers and volunteers we constructed a $500 van to be off-road worthy, hold plenty of trash bags, and make the occasional fix with our tools along the way.
#leathermantools #gambler500
